description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 183 residential dwellings, comprising a mix of housing and flats including 1 studio unit, 25 one-bedroom units, 54 two-bedroom units, 92 three-bedroom units, 10 four- bedroom units and 1 five-bedroom unit, with associated amenity space, landscaping, new access road and car parking.
